Package ast.cexp

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CExp
    This abstract class represents a comparison expression in the abstract syntax tree (AST).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EqCExp
    This class represents an equality comparison expression in the abstract syntax tree (AST).
    GCExp
    This class represents a "greater than" comparison expression in the abstract syntax tree (AST).
    GeqCExp
    This class represents a "greater than or equal" comparison expression in the abstract syntax tree (AST).
    LCExp
    This class represents a "less than" comparison expression in the abstract syntax tree (AST).
    LeqCExp
    This class represents a "less than or equal" comparison expression in the abstract syntax tree (AST).
